title: Abbys.Ultimate.Dance.Competition.S02E03.Gods.and.Mortals.mp4
description:
Abby's Ultimate Dance Competition - Gods and Mortals

Abby is the dance goddess of the week and the dancers strive to attain dance immortality when the theme is "Gods and Mortals." There are nine dancers left and the performers in last week's bottom group struggle to prove that they deserve to be in the competition. The skill is "Power" and this week's challenge winner and her mom get to make all the dance assignments and quickly discover holding the power isn't always easy. One mom gets extreme when she overhears the others mothers talking about her daughter's weaknesses.
